HSBC Bank (Europe)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from HSBC Bank plc)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"HSBC Bank plc" redirects here. It is not to be confused with HSBC Bank.

HSBC Bank plc





Type

Subsidiary


Industry
Finance and insurance


Founded
1865 in Birmingham, Great Britain


Headquarters
London, United Kingdom



Key people

Jonathan Symonds
(Chairman)
António Simões
(CEO)


