Product finder APIs for HSBC, first direct and M&S Bank.




















HSBC Group developer portal > Open Banking APIs > Product finder

                Product finder
            

These APIs provide users with detailed information about personal (PCA) and business (BCA) current accounts, lending products for small to medium enterprises (SMEL) and commercial credit cards (CCC) offered by HSBC, first direct and M&S Bank in the United Kingdom.












                Documentation and sandbox 

Key features:

Name of each product
Product features
Eligibility description
Pricing, fees and interest rates








                   How do they work?
            

These APIs are exposed as REST APIs using a swagger definition file that can be downloaded in the documentation. The data provided through the associated APIs relates to the UK only, and is prepared to the Open API, data format and security standards as maintained by the Open Banking Implementation Entity (OBIE).
                    In addition to our regulatory obligations we’ve included extensions to allow you to search by product segment. The extended functionality may not fully adhere to the non-functional requirements of the regulator.

 Personal current account (PCA) products:
You can request information about all the PCA products currently available from HSBC UK, first direct and M&S Bank in the UK. We’ve also included an extension to allow you to search PCA products by product segment.

Business current accounts (BCA) products:
You can request information about all the BCA products currently available from HSBC in the UK. We’ve also included an extension to allow you to search BCA products by product segment.

Small and medium sized enterprise lending (SMEL) products:
You can request information about lending products intended for small and medium sized enterprises available from HSBC in the UK. We’ve also included an extension to allow you to search SME lending products by product segment.

Commercial credit cards (CCC) products:
You can request information about the commercial credit cards available from HSBC in the UK. We’ve also included an extension to allow you to search for commercial credit cards by product segment.

Product information for other countries is currently unavailable.


                Who can use them?
            

Use of the APIs and any related data is subject to the terms of the Open Licence and subject to terms and conditions.


                How much do they cost?
            

There are no charges for using these APIs. You don't have to register.









                    Documentation and sandbox 







Key features:

Name of each product
Product features
Eligibility description
Pricing, fees and interest rates



























Open Banking APIs for HSBC, first direct and M&S Bank.




















HSBC Group developer portal

The definitive source of information and technical specifications for the APIs made available by members of the HSBC Group including HSBC UK, first direct and M&S Bank. 
Public websites: 
This website is for software developers. If you think you are on the wrong site, please visit the relevant public website. 









 



            Open Banking APIs
        

Open Banking APIs are free to use and provide up-to-date information about the location and facilities of our branches and ATMs, detailed product information for personal and business current accounts, lending to small to medium enterprises and commercial credit cards.You can use this data to build applications that make it easier for personal and business customers to compare what’s offered by different banks. The data provided through the associated APIs relates to the UK only, and is prepared to the Open API, data format and security standards as maintained by the Open Banking Implementation Entity (OBIE).









Branch locator

                    Get the locations of and facilities at our branches.

                







ATM locator

                    Get the locations of all our ATMs.

                







Product finder

                    Current accounts, SME lending products and commercial credit cards.
                










Branch locator

                    Get the locations of and facilities at our branches.

                









ATM locator

                    Get the locations of all our ATMs.
                









Product finder

                    Current accounts, SME lending products and commercial credit cards.
                









                    What we're working on
                
We continue to lead the way forward into a new era of open banking. We'll keep improving and extending the APIs so that you can carry on creating applications to help all banking customers.

                By early 2018 we’ll deliver new APIs that will allow personal customers and small businesses to share their data securely with other banks and trusted third parties. This is nothing short of a revolution in banking and will change the face of financial services forever.

































